Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.79,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,They said they got a fiefdom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:10.89,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,so I was expecting, well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.89,0:00:12.49,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,This is the middle of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:14.81,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to be rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:18.06,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,but I wonder about the previous owner,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:19.76,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,letting this place go like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:24.59,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,The old master died ten years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.59,0:00:26.44,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,and since he had no heirs,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.44,0:00:29.74,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,the land went into the \Nkeeping of the queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:34.44,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.81,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,The young folks have \Nall given up their land
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:39.40,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,and gone to the cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:42.16,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,All you've got left are \Nold-timers like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:44.26,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,scrabbling along to \Nkeep the land tilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:45.88,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This region is actually renowned for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.88,0:00:48.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,its dry land, since it \Nproduces great grapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:50.59,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:55.87,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Already acting like a \Nfeudal lord, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:00:58.80,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not acting! \NI really am a feudal lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:01.32,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,The lord here is Saito, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.32,0:01:04.64,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Saito Chevalier De Hiraga... \NWhat else was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.94,0:01:07.98,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Saito Chevalier De Hiraga De Ornierés.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:09.58,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:13.85,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I was pretty shocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:15.89,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to see \Nyou here, Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:18.81,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you're \Ngoing to become a queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:21.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I wanted to \Nask about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:23.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.62,0:01:25.43,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't decided yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.11,0:01:30.65,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:31.82,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:34.07,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,Sister wants to hatch an egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.40,0:01:35.40,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,An egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.97,0:01:37.77,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,I think she's talking \Nabout becoming pregnant
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:39.37,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,with someone's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:41.50,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-Pregnant?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:43.35,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be pregnant, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:48.17,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think I should go practice \Nmy sword fighting techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.61,0:01:50.30,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:51.18,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:54.43,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be ditched!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.85,0:01:57.13,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.69,0:02:02.37,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,The new lords sure are \Na vigorous bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.77,0:02:05.90,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice to see a \Nsuccessor born soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:42.00,Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,1}The Maidens of De Ornierés
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:54.52,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite a nice hall \Nfor a country mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.11,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Those look delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:01.57,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.82,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,The way to a man's heart \Nis through his stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:05.18,CRZero,Illococoo,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:10.83,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,This is more a dump than a basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.10,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all these books!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:16.83,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha is going to love this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:18.82,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she's really in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:20.26,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,the mood for reading right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:24.14,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen her like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:27.35,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.08,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,She came here because
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.78,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,she wants to be close to Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.75,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,She won't have any freedom once \Nshe ascends to the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:34.97,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,But here she won't be able
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:37.32,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,to avoid seeing those two together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.69,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:41.28,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,That's love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.28,0:04:42.93,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,You know on a rational level,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.35,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't help yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:46.88,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.45,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:54.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so laid back \Nabout this whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.57,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally got our own house,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:59.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,but we might as well \Nstill be at the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.66,0:05:01.61,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Those are so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.61,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:07.06,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.89,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:10.47,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.38,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.07,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you staring at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.81,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking \Nabout how happy I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:20.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you smile makes me happier
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.54,0:05:22.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,than anything else in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.30,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking \Nabout all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.34,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.88,0:05:30.19,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,When I first came here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.76,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to go back to \Nmy world all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:35.55,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,but now, I feel like not \Ngoing back would be okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:37.55,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.32,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.55,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't feel like \Nthis with another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.13,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:45.31,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:46.76,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:57.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:05:59.53,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:03.22,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just sorry they're so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:10.07,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,If that wasn't it, \Ndoes that mean it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:17.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you for a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.66,0:06:18.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:20.03,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Will you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.03,0:06:23.53,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,"The little meow-meow wants to be \Nteased by the big meow-meow, meow."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.35,0:06:28.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course that's too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.84,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be gentle if I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:33.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:41.01,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The little meow-meow wants to be \Nteased by the big meow-meow, meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,And can you tell me how?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.69,0:06:46.32,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.78,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,You can do what you like, Saito. Meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.15,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch is ready, meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:57.15,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,This idiot made me say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:58.89,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:06:59.79,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.79,0:07:04.07,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.12,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,That was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:09.08,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,It really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:10.29,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:14.61,CRZero,Old man,0000,0000,0000,,There is someone here \Nto see Miss Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.61,0:07:15.71,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,To see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:17.22,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:24.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.26,0:07:25.93,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, little Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:29.08,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard all about the indulgent \Nthings you've been doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:30.95,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.35,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving school with a man \Nbefore getting married,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:35.99,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,trying to live in a villa with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:40.37,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,Don't expect me to ever acknowledge \Nsuch a filthy relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.37,0:07:42.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to listen to that from
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.11,0:07:43.54,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,someone who failed to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:46.68,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,You'd make the House of Vallière
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:47.87,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,the laughingstock of the country
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:49.66,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,if the third daughter \Nlived with someone
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:51.15,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,with a dubious background!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:52.80,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.87,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito is not dubious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.19,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,He is a real nobleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.56,0:07:58.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,He received this land as a reward
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.20,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,from Her Majesty for \Nsaving His Holiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.22,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care, we're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:02.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Elder sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:06.62,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,You have no business \Ncalling me your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.43,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But I plan on visiting \Nyour mother and father
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:12.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.75,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make Louise happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.75,0:08:17.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I will make her happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.36,0:08:18.64,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.22,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way a daughter of Vallière
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.52,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,is going to get married to a
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:25.60,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,faux-nobleman who can't \Neven speak properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:27.62,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.89,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I will make Saito into \Na proper nobleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.17,0:08:34.69,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If he was a nobleman who you \Ncould take to any court,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:37.83,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,there'd be no problem, right, Eleanor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.80,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never take "no" for an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.16,0:08:46.29,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:47.81,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,Cram the proper behavior \Nfor a nobleman
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.24,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,into his head before I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.83,0:08:53.14,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not satisfied, you're \Ncoming straight home with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.83,0:08:55.46,CRZero,Eleanor,0000,0000,0000,,Is that understood, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.61,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:06.03,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, "Please teach \Nme proper manners
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.03,0:09:07.81,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,from the ground up."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:08.45,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:10.31,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.31,0:09:11.33,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:14.19,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to make you noble, \Nfrom top to bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's going to be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:17.65,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,raise a single complaint against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:22.84,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:26.18,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You bow like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.56,0:09:27.47,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Now you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:30.11,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:33.77,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,May I have the pleasure of this dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.53,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,The way you extend \Nyour hand is common.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.82,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,The way I extend my hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:41.50,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Walk slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.66,0:09:43.60,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:46.00,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.00,0:09:46.95,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Moo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.52,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.59,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,And stop mooing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.89,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:57.48,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I was planning on staying over,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:59.11,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,but it looks like they're quite busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:01.18,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,And we did get the grand \Ntour of the place already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:04.04,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't it too late to leave now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.96,0:10:06.26,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:10.65,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,We might as well take \Nher up on the offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:12.84,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot, Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.89,0:10:20.02,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta, tell those two we said bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:21.83,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.44,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.18,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You've got absolutely no class!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.82,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:30.76,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:31.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:32.44,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.97,0:10:34.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.85,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's weird that you're \Ntrying to change my nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:40.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,But my sister, Eleanor...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.61,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going to live with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.10,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Not your sister, Eleanor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:48.15,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anybody \Nto make fun of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if people make fun of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:51.65,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no reason we have
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.30,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,to go that far just to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.30,0:10:54.20,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.20,0:10:55.69,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.44,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,you need to act like a nobleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.43,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll be taken home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.82,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.82,0:11:01.94,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying your sister's opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.78,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,is more important to \Nyou than my feelings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:05.71,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not a nobleman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:09.17,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:10.80,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I could say the same about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.28,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep in the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:17.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,same room as someone who's not noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:19.16,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Go find yourself another room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:22.63,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,This is my house, and I'll sleep \Nwhere I damn well please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:36.17,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I probably shouldn't \Nhave said those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.28,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pal,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:44.25,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,what's with these dusty lodgings?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I figured the basement is \Nwhere I belong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.54,0:11:48.18,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,since I'm not a lord and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.18,0:11:50.19,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you sound so bitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:53.11,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this lord talk, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:56.54,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Can't she just be with \Nme because she loves me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:59.00,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Just the way I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.39,0:12:04.37,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:06.34,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Is even this chair \Nmaking a fool of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:10.01,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:16.68,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:19.85,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.32,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.79,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.22,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.32,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.34,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some sort of hidden room?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:46.81,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:58.02,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember this hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:06.10,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Sa—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.30,0:13:12.10,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What's Her Majesty doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.76,0:13:34.68,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your Majesty?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.10,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.46,0:13:41.87,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.34,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:48.36,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I opened my closet and then \NI saw you in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:51.37,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I said your \Nname out loud in surprise,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.79,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:52.36,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:56.42,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like there is some kind \Nof spell cast on this mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.36,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,and the mirror in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.43,0:14:03.14,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,H-How about first we find \Nyou something to wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.85,0:14:09.25,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,But I really was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.12,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Who would have thought my bedroom
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:13.31,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,in the castle is connected \Nto this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.87,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.12,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Looking at how this room is built,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.97,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I think it might have \Nbeen for a mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.97,0:14:20.91,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,A mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.91,0:14:21.77,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:24.54,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,The couple lived upstairs
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.78,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,and the secret trysts were held here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:29.51,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Trysts...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.11,0:14:32.58,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I would have never imagined that my \Ngrandfather had a side like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.58,0:14:34.22,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,He was regarded as a very strict king.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:38.38,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose he had little choice \Nin who he had to marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.84,0:14:43.12,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I was also told by my mother \Nthat I should marry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.93,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:46.66,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Marriage...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:50.85,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I've already given up on ever \Nmarrying someone I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.60,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Still, when it comes down to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:56.37,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,it's hard to convince my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.07,0:14:59.01,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Marrying for my country...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.55,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:04.75,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to say in \Na situation like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:07.86,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,So you won't tell me that \NI shouldn't get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:10.18,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.78,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,You're in love with Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.03,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:16.89,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,...what I was expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.15,0:15:20.12,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you don't want to, \Nthen you shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.63,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,It's weird to marry \Nsomeone you don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.10,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that out of pity?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.73,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:32.98,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.96,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's only once in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.52,0:15:52.72,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,if you would meet with me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:56.14,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.25,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:07.03,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's meet here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.60,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But I... I have Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.11,0:16:12.24,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.30,0:16:15.70,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,But the other me keeps saying
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:20.01,CRZero,Henrietta,0000,0000,0000,,that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:25.96,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.79,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:31.56,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fight with your girl again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.56,0:16:33.45,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:35.87,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, was Louise down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:36.97,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.14,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Then she ran out with red eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.96,0:16:41.28,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Could she have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:44.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.01,0:16:46.48,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,About the princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.48,0:16:47.65,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That was just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:50.84,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you that \Nshe feels the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.68,0:16:54.10,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, I always thought
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.98,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I knew everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:57.66,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.35,0:16:59.82,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:00.73,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.84,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I didn't notice until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.04,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.68,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give her too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:11.60,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:16.70,CRZero,Derflinger,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you go after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:21.25,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the right to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.28,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.44,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:34.01,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the weather today just \Nbeautiful, Miss Vallière?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:35.29,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.60,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she ran away with Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.30,0:17:42.94,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry we kept you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:46.74,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,But, by the same token, \Nwe were actually able to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:48.39,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your best
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:49.75,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,so that you won't regret anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:17:59.24,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:04.08,CRZero,Montmorency,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, \Ndressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.27,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Did you and Saito already \Nhave a marital spat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:09.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have a spat. \NI broke up with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:12.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I can't compete \Nagainst the queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.61,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It turns out I don't have many places
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.61,0:18:17.24,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,to go at times like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.09,0:18:30.46,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,How did it end up like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.26,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.39,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:41.65,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:45.94,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious about leaving Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:48.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:52.59,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll take him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.59,0:18:53.14,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:55.70,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the future queen of Gallia,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:58.28,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,so I can have whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.02,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.84,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You mean you'd force him to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:04.92,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.86,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,And if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:09.86,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:12.60,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I could marry him, too, \Nif that was my wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.27,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:17.97,CRZero,Tabitha,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.65,0:19:22.33,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha, wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.48,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:33.95,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Kirche?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:40.27,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why Tabitha said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:44.47,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha understands Queen \NHenrietta's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.18,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,They're one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.37,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.48,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,You're not free to love
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.47,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,when you've got a kingdom \Non your shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.58,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,That makes them that much more \Nscary when they're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:58.01,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,They'll throw all their \Npride away and go for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:02.45,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,even if it might not make Saito happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:05.25,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,or if it meant turning \Nfriends into foes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:07.31,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,If someone would go
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.54,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,that far for you, I guess even \NSaito can't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.69,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready for that, Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:17.45,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking that if Saito \Nreally did love the queen,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.36,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I ought to respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:23.49,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if that's all it \Ntakes for you to back off,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:26.10,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,then that's how serious \Nyour feelings were.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:27.07,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:30.61,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,To me, Saito is... Saito is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.90,0:20:32.42,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Winning at love is
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.42,0:20:35.00,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,about being honest with yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.32,CRZero,Kirche,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I like to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:49.36,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go back to my old world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.69,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't be with Louise,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:53.26,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,there's no reason for me to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:54.90,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:58.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:03.52,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:08.23,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one for me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.44,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.44,0:21:11.82,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care how the \Nqueen feels about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:14.06,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:17.18,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.31,0:21:20.99,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Just this once, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.49,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,That's the face I love seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:24.75,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:28.25,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who \Ncan make you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:29.21,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:32.17,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.75,CRZero,Siesta,0000,0000,0000,,What is this room, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.75,0:21:41.88,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's haunted, so I'm exorcising it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.88,0:21:42.55,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Nail!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:43.68,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:54.33,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for not \Nholding it down properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.69,0:23:29.25,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saito, what's a hot spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:31.75,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,What, a place where you feel very good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:34.71,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,And being naked there \Nis the proper behavior?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:36.51,CRZero,Saito,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Trouble at the Outdoor Bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:40.01,CRZero,Louise,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be naked with anybody else!
